of Anti-Gravity Propulsion."

00:00:45.380 --> 00:00:46.940 align:middle line:10%
Paul, welcome to
"Beyond Belief."

00:00:46.940 --> 00:00:47.915 align:middle line:10%
>>PAUL LAVIOLETTE: Glad
to be here, George.

