a technological breakthrough?

00:27:41.460 --> 00:27:43.140 align:middle line:84%
By the turn of the
century, Morgan

00:27:43.140 --> 00:27:44.910 align:middle line:84%
had become one of
the most powerful men

00:27:44.910 --> 00:27:47.970 align:middle line:84%
in the world controlling the
US electrical and railroad

00:27:47.970 --> 00:27:52.950 align:middle line:84%
