net worth of $68.3 million.

00:27:52.950 --> 00:27:55.650 align:middle line:84%
Morgan initially financed
Tesla's wireless tower,

00:27:55.650 --> 00:27:57.870 align:middle line:84%
believing it was designed
to send communications

00:27:57.870 --> 00:27:59.140 align:middle line:90%
